pr_title: Simultaneous creation of summary files and testing of Dandisets
pr_body:
The following pull request is the final update to DANDIArchiveShowcase which allows for creating summary files on the go as testing is being conducted . 

### New Flags ( also reflected in the README.md )

+ ```--test_docker```  : (Test Dandisets / Update Readme) using the NWBE container
+ ```--create_summary``` : Create summaries for files which do not contain one
